You surely can call this as #lockdowndiaries because well since I have come back from the trip I myself have given myself a small break
and I did this to bring back that old Muskaan who used to participate in painting , elocution and do all those school events because it used to give her happiness.  That Muskaan was lost in the last year wherein I had to leave quite many things for my mental peace and went in a situation wherein I'll leave participating in anything that comes in but now I have done entries in 8 events also trying to handle things subtly and alone. This is the result of it I know its not a master piece or something but its really precious to me for me to discover me.
#painting #aesthetic #cityscape #skyline

latestIgtvVideos.title: Thank u my 3.5k family 🥺❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
guys there was a time wherin procrastination was a part of life and I was in a phase of depression after an account of mine which worked for 3years with 2.6k followers got hacked after that I had lost hope of gaining the strength of consistency or posting anything on social media , but today I feel super overwhelmed it's although a small number for people but for me it's a whole big , large , super strong family of three thousand five hundred mates !
thank you so much for accepting the way I am and taking at times the overloaded content too ! 
love you !! and keep supporting your girl ! 
I live for you all ❤️🥺

latestIgtvVideos.title: Ucchiyaan deewaran
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
this song has all my heart ❤️
@bilalsaeed_music 
@mominamustehsan 
@desimusicfactory 
Translation- 
Kadi Tu Es Gali De Hi Agle Mod Te Milda Si
Tainu Khabar Si Sari Ke Haal Jo Mere Dil Da Si
Tu Bhul Gaya Sareyan Oh Galan Te Main Na Bhulli Ve Sajjna
Ke Ajj Mainu Vekh’ke Ve Hath Te Tere Cha Dulli Na Sajjna

There were times when you met me around the corner of this very street.
You were also very well aware of the condition of my heart.
You may have forgotten all of this, but I haven’t forgotten it, dear.
Although today, like old times, you didn’t spill the tea on your hands out of excitement, after you saw me.

Vekhi Teri Wafa Sajjna Bhull Gayi Si Main Raah Sajjna
Jandi Jandi Kho Gayi Sah Khaba De Vich Tere
Main Tahin Uchiyan Deewaran Rakhiyan Is Dil De Char Chufere
Nale Sambh Ke Rakhiyan Si Koi Dil Ch Na La Le Dere

Seeing your faithfulness, I forgot my way, sweetie.
And I lost myself in your dreams while I was leaving.
That’s why I’ve kept the walls high and firm around the boundaries of my heart.
I kept my heart in safekeeping so that nobody could come into my heart and stay in it.

Han Mera Pehlan Vi Dil Tuteya Phir Todeya Tu Ik Wari
Kyun Dil Di Deewaran Te Main Tere Layi Banayi Bari

Earlier too one time, my heart had been broken. Then again, you broke it.
Why did I build a door (entrance) in my heart’s walls and allow you to my heart?
#ucchiyandeewaran
#baari2 #punjabi
